review: I had to get used to the taste as it is bit less sweet then I would like it but the better..I was searching for yogurt brand that does NOT have in the ingredient list any gums of any sort as those have bad rap. in terms of influence on your system and how they affect immune system as such. It was pretty tiring to check all the labels of all the yogurts out there and even many organic ones do contain those things that I would rather not have in my body.Here is the ingredients list of this yougurt and this is why I like itno JUNK!Just your milk, cream, fruits, cane sugar!!! yes, cane NOT Corn Syrup., fruit pectin that is a good thingand lemon juice and then a ton of all good bacteria... all you need is here: and nothing else!Pasteurized Skim Milk, Pasteurized Cream, Black Cherries, Cane Sugar, Fruit Pectin, Lemon Juice, Live Active Cultures Live Active Cultures: S. Thermophilus, L. Delbrueckii Subsp. Bulgaricus, B. Lactis, L. Acidophilus, L. Delbrueckii Subsp. Lactis
